title: Silence-Heart-Nest Vegetarian Restaurant
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Indian, Take-out
description: A Sri Chimoy inspired veggie restaurant serving vegetarian and vegan food since 1986. The extensive menu features a variety of egg scrambles and breakfast items served all day plus salads, sandwiches, veggieburgers, hot plates, and more. Bargain breakfast menu offered weekdays before 11am.
